{"tid":995685,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[莫縮叔台] 審判之眼：死神的遺言 (PS4)","createTime":"2019-01-25T15:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T16:08:15.000Z","uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e528816b3924fe54c655fb707b55b66f898933b2","tid":995685,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"[莫縮叔台] 審判之眼：死神的遺言 (PS4)<br />\n<br />\n莫縮叔遊戲台<br />\n每個星期五、六、日晚上，<br />\n跟大家一邊傾計，一邊打機<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fmokuncle%2F&d=%2FenRMUSmyxzXWOGUtpTEOQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=4ed92185\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/</a><br />\n<br />\n主角八神隆之過去曾任殺人案嫌疑人大久保新平的辯護律師，當時在輿論極為不利的情況下，漂亮地獲得無罪判決而一時聲名大噪，但當事人被釋放後不久，竟犯下殘殺同居女友並且對住所公寓縱火之罪行，八神的評價因此一落千丈，並且被大眾稱為「縱放兇惡殺人兇手的冒牌律師」，也讓他失去了先前建立的一切聲譽，並自此離開了律師的工作。<br />\n<br />\n事件3年後，離開律師一行的八神在神室町開設了一家偵探事務所，為了餬口各種工作都接，此時一件自源田法律事務接下關於神室町連續殺人事件的委託，開始改變了他的命運。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/06/JUDGE_EYES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F06%2FJUDGE_EYES.jpg&h=bf6ed16e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(來源:維基百科)<br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n莫縮叔Facebook Page: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMokUncle&d=%2FenRMUSmyxzXWOGUtpTEOQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=03245f76\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle</a>"},{"pid":"addb9e6111859ee5747b910c958f001d3354ade5","tid":995685,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef67cd53352271062915d9df6ce54ab42be5fa3","tid":995685,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:08:15.000